NG0801:2: ma ra na kro d+ha ka pa la gu h+ya tan+t+ra na ma /
NG0801:4: bdud khros pa thod pa'i 'phreng ba can gsang ba'i rgyud ces bya ba //
NG0801:5: dpal he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0801:6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
NG0801:7: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po nyid 'og min gyi
NG0801:8: gnas rdo rje btsun mo'i b+ha ga la dges pa
NG0801:9: chen po'i tshul du bzhugs so //
NG0801:10: de'i tshe de'i dus nas zhe sdang gdug pa'i pa'i 'bras bu mngon du gyur pa ni /
NG0801:11: bar du gcod pas na bdud /
NG0801:12: rab tu gtum pa'i cha byad can gyi bdud de ni /
NG0801:13: sems can rnams kyi sha dang khrag rlon pa za zhing 'thung la /
NG0801:14: 'khor pho nya dang phyag brnyan gyi bdud bcu ni /
NG0801:15: rab tu mi srun cing skye 'gro rnams kyi dbugs rngub ste sha rus za la /
NG0801:16: don snying rnams ni gtso bo stobs pa'i tshul gyis
NG0801:17: rab tu rgyug go / de'i tshe dpal chen po
NG0801:18: nyid sems cad rnams la thugs brtse bas thugs rje
NG0801:20: bdud de nyid kyi sems kyi rnam par la dpal chen po nyid du rang snang ste /
NG0801:21: gdul bya dus la bab pas na de'o //
NG0801:23: dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0801:24: sems can la gnod pa ma byed /
NG0801:25: srog gcad pas ni mthar dmyal bar 'gro bar 'gyur ro //
NG0801:28: sems can la gnod pa mi byed na /
NG0801:29: pha dang ma la gnod pa byed dgos la /
NG0801:30: srog mi gcad du zas sha khrag 'thung ba lags so //
NG0801:31: dmyal ba bgyi ba ni gang lags /
NG0801:35: gleng gzhi dris lan dang bcas pa'i le'u ste dang
NG0801:36: po'o // // yang dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa
NG0801:37: // sems can la gnod pa byas pas ni mi bde ba 'byung ba yin la /
NG0801:38: srog gcad pas ni tshe thung ngo *//
NG0801:39: dmyal pa bya ba ni na pa dang */
NG0801:42: 'jigs shing skyi g.ya' ba'i sdug bsngal mang po nyams su myong bar 'gyur ro //
NG0801:46: nongs pa mi bzad pa de lta na gnod pa gang la bgyid /
NG0801:47: srog mi gcod cing sha khrag gi 'tshal ma spangs na /
NG0801:48: 'tshal ba'i zas gang la bgyi zhes gsol to //
NG0801:49: dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0801:50: gnod pa byed par 'dod na yang */
NG0801:51: nag po'i phyogs rnams la byos shig @#//
NG0801:52: srog gcod na yang mtshams med pa lnga byed pa dang */
NG0801:53: dkon mchog gsum gyi sku dgra rnams kyi gcod par
NG0801:54: bya ba yin pas na chod cig / zas su
NG0801:55: mam sa btab pa'i gtor ma dang */
NG0801:56: nyams pa sdig can de dag gi sha khrag la zo zhig / ces bka' stsal pas /
NG0801:57: bdud de rab tu dga' che ste /
NG0801:58: bcom ldan 'das la 'di skad ces gsol to //
NG0801:59: kye ma sngon chad ma rig ma rtogs nas //
NG0801:60: sha zos khrag 'thung las ngan bgyis //
NG0801:61: bag chags sgrib pa byang gyur cig / slad nas mi bgyid dam cha yis //
NG0801:62: dpa' bo chen pos dbang rtags gsol //
NG0801:64: dpal chen po'i zhabs la gtugs na de nyid du
NG0801:65: 'dug go / de'i tshe dpal chen po nyid kyis
NG0801:66: / badzra ka ta ri a b+hi shiny+tsa mam /
NG0801:68: dgra bgegs kyi lus btul ba'i phyir lag pa g.yas par shel dkar gyi gri byin no //
NG0801:69: ka pa li ma la a b+hi shiny+tsa mi /
NG0801:71: dpal chen po'i 'khor gyi bsgrub mchog rnams la gtong
NG0801:72: dang grogs mi zad par bya ba'i phyir thod pa'i
NG0801:73: 'phreng ba dbang rtags su byin no //
NG0801:75: bdud bstan pa la bzhag nas dbang bskur de dam
NG0801:76: phog pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o // // yang dpal
NG0801:78: phyi rabs kyi rnal 'byor pas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir bdud nyid bsgrub pa'i thabs bshad kyis /
NG0801:79: legs par nyon cig / e ma ho /
NG0801:82: mda' gang ldan pa'i man+dal la //
NG0801:83: dur khrod thal bas spar khab gtang *//
NG0801:84: gdug pa'i rjes na lta phyir ro //
NG0801:85: de yi dbus su gru gsum ste /
NG0801:86: rtse mo lho 'am dgra phyogs bstan //
NG0801:87: nang du ro sol dug gis byug / mnyes pa'i
NG0801:88: rdzas su 'di dag bsag / lug nag gsob ni
NG0801:89: legs rgyangs la // rwa la dar snas brgyan pa dang *//
NG0801:90: skye ru ming rus bris la gdags //
NG0801:91: bshos bu nag po khru gang la //
NG0801:92: mda' nag dar nag btags pa gzugs //
NG0801:93: mda' la ling ka ming byang gdags //
NG0801:94: gtor ma bdud rtsi rag ta ste //
NG0801:95: rang nyid bdud chas ldan par bya'o //
NG0801:96: bsgrub pa'i rdzas ni 'di dag go / dam rdzas
NG0801:97: ni 'di dag go / dam rdzas bsnyen pa'i tshul
NG0801:98: dang 'dra // bsnyen pa'i dus kyi bshos bu btang *//
NG0801:99: bshos nag bsam pa byas la bzhag / khyad par
NG0801:100: du ni 'di rnams bsag / gzas pa'i rdzas bsdus
NG0801:101: ling ga bya // mgo dang snying ka lte ba ru //
NG0801:102: rus dang ming dang bla gdags gsum //
NG0801:103: gling ma'i byang bu mtshon gang la //
NG0801:104: rme ba'i khrag gis bris la gzhug / skye nas mkhar nag dag gis gdags //
NG0801:105: lcags phur bdud du skyes pa cig / 'brub khung lho yi zur la gzugs //
NG0801:106: ling ga 'brub khung nang bsdu ste //
NG0801:107: 'khar nag phur pa de la gdags //
NG0801:108: nyungs kar la sogs thun rdzas la //
NG0801:109: thun du bsngags te brdeg par @#//
NG0801:111: mkha' lding nyi mas 'jigs pa'i gsob //
NG0801:112: brang 'gro'i gsob dang lbas gsob gsum //
NG0801:113: nang du ling ga gzhug pa ste //
NG0801:114: ri rtse ri zur chu la bskur //
NG0801:115: las mtha' gnan pa'i rdzas su bsngags //
NG0801:116: li ri su tra'i khrag la ni //
NG0801:117: ha la'i dug rnams sbyar la mngag / nye ring khang khyim phyogs su 'phang *//
NG0801:121: zor bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum pa'o //  // yang dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0801:122: de ltar rdzas rnams tshogs gyur nas //
NG0801:123: phyi rabs rnal 'byor pa de ni //
NG0801:124: bdag nyid bdud du bsgom pa des //
NG0801:125: sku mdog nag po chen po la //
NG0801:126: zhal gcig phyag kyang gnyis pa ste //
NG0801:127: g.yas pa shel gyi gri khug 'dzin //
NG0801:128: g.yon pa spar pa gdengs pa ste //
NG0801:129: dgra bo'i srog snying gcod par bsam //
NG0801:131: dam nyams yud tsam gyis bkug nas //
NG0801:132: bdag nyid mdun du sgrol ba ste //
NG0801:133: don snying bdag la stobs par bsam //
NG0801:134: de la sngags ni 'di yin te //
NG0801:135: ma ra na thum shig sod //
NG0801:136: ma ra na a mu ka bam sod //
NG0801:137: ma ra na snying tul pri sha stam b+ha ya sod sod /
NG0801:138: de skad ces ni bzlas pa yi //
NG0801:139: rtags kyi rnam pa 'di rnams so //
NG0801:140: mi nag rta nag bzhon pa 'am //
NG0801:141: rta nag khyi nag mi nag dang *//
NG0801:142: bdud po dngos su 'ong yang srid /
NG0801:143: khang pa 'tsheg pa 'am sgo ni 'tshig dang 'khrog / bya rog tshogs chen 'du ba'o //
NG0801:147: rtags bstan pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o //  // yang dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0801:148: de ltar rtags rnams mthong gyur nas //
NG0801:149: ling ga gsol tu bcug nas ni //
NG0801:150: 'bru khung gting du gzhug par bya //
NG0801:151: de la thun rnams brab cing gsob //
NG0801:152: ra lug 'bri g.yag ri dgas sam //
NG0801:153: bya byi'u la sogs bsad pa'am //
NG0801:154: dngos su bsad cing rmi ba'am //
NG0801:155: bdag la don snying stobs pa'o //
NG0801:156: de ltar byung na las gzhug bsdu /
NG0801:159: sgrub pa rtags dang drod gzung ba'i le'u+u ste lnga
NG0801:160: pa'o // // yang dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa
NG0801:161: / spyan drangs nas ni mchod pa dbul //
NG0801:162: las la mngag cing 'phrin las bcol /
NG0801:164: gru gsum mthing nag 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0801:165: bdud kyi rgyal po gshegs su gsol //
NG0801:166: yag sha 'bar ba gshegs su gsol //
NG0801:167: bdud kyi bdud cig khyod las lhag pa med //
NG0801:168: 'gro ba mi yi bdud du khyod bskor te //
NG0801:169: dgra bo'i bdud du khyod las lhag pa med //
NG0801:170: mi zad yun gyi mtha' yang mi gtong la //
NG0801:171: rgyab rten dpung gnyen du yang khyod las mi tshol du //
NG0801:172: mthun pa'i dam rdzas mchod pa dam pa dang *//
NG0801:173: dgra bo'i sha khrag mchod par bzhes su gsol //
NG0801:177: sa ma ya i mam b+ha ling ta dgra bgegs la kha ram kha hi /
NG0801:179: pany+tsa a mr-i ta kha ram kha hi /
NG0801:180: de nas 'phrin las bcol ba ni /
NG0801:182: dam tshig chen po'i dus la bab //
NG0801:183: srog gi gshed du bskul ba ni //
NG0801:184: bdud rgyal thod pa'i 'phreng ba can //
NG0801:185: sku ni mthing nag chen po la //
NG0801:186: chibs su bdud rta nag po chibs //
NG0801:187: lcags mdung nag po g.yas na thogs //
NG0801:188: g.yon na thod pa'i 'phreng ba bgrang *//
NG0801:189: thod pa skam po'i dbu rgyan can //
NG0801:190: mi lpags rlon pa sku la gsol //
NG0801:191: rgyu ma sbrul gyis lus brgyan cing */
NG0801:192: khrag dang zhag gi thig le can //
NG0801:193: mche ba gtsigs shing gsus po che //
NG0801:194: tsit+ta'i khrag la longs spyod pas /
NG0801:195: khyod ni srog bdag chen po ste //
NG0801:196: sring cig rdo rje re ma ti //
NG0801:197: ming sring gnyis kyi dam bcas pa //
NG0801:198: dam bcas bzhin du phrin las mdzod //
NG0801:199: sngon tshe dpal chen he ru kas //
NG0801:200: dbang rtags thod pa byin nas ni //
NG0801:201: bka' stsal dam phog mdzad pa'i tshe //
NG0801:202: de tshe khas blangs dam bcas pa //
NG0801:203: bsgrub mchog bskyang bar dam bcas shing *//
NG0801:204: dgra bo bsgral bar khas blangs pas //
NG0801:205: dam nyams bsgral pa'i dus la bab /
NG0801:206: khyod ni srog bdag chen po ste //
NG0801:207: dgra bo'i srog la mnga' thang mdzod //
NG0801:208: srog dbug long zhig sa ma ya //
NG0801:209: srog rtsa chod cig sa ma ya /
NG0801:210: khyod kyi zas skal khams gsum sha yin te //
NG0801:211: dam nyams sha ni zan du gsol //
NG0801:212: dgra bo'i sha la kha ram kha hi //
NG0801:214: khyod kyi skom ni skye 'gro'i khrag yin te //
NG0801:215: dgra bo'i khrag ni skom du gsol //
NG0801:216: dgra bo'i khrag la pi pa to //
NG0801:218: khyod ni dmag dpon chen po ste //
NG0801:219: sa gzhi thams cad dmag gis khengs //
NG0801:220: dgra bo'i yul du dmag 'dren gyis /
NG0801:221: dmag sna drongs shig thod 'phreng can //
NG0801:222: dmag gzhug rtul cig thod 'phreng can //
NG0801:223: go mtshon stor cig thod 'phreng can //
NG0801:224: dmag dpung bskyed la ru mtshon phyor //
NG0801:225: dgra bo'i yul du dmag drongs la //
NG0801:226: dam nyams dgra po'i bla mkhar shig / bla shing chod la bla rdo rkus //
NG0801:227: bla chu hub kyi thob la shog / khyod kyi dam tshig dus la bab //
NG0801:228: dus la bab bo sa ma ya //
NG0801:229: ma g.yel bcol ba'i 'phrin las mdzod //
NG0801:230: de skad ces ni bskul bya ba //
NG0801:231: de nas pho nya rab bkye ba //
NG0801:232: shes pa ling ga dag la bstim //
NG0801:234: de yi thugs kyi sprul pa las //
NG0801:235: bka' nyan pho nya'i tshogs chen ni //
NG0801:236: steng gi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:237: bdud kyi rgyal po khro bdag 'bar ba rje //
NG0801:238: phyag na bdud kyi spar shad 'bar ba bsnams //
NG0801:239: steng gi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog /
NG0801:240: ma ra ya dzahdzah che ge mo ma ra na
NG0801:242: shar gyi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:243: bdud kyi rgyal po ma ha khro bdag rje //
NG0801:244: phyag na bdud zhags nag po bsnams //
NG0801:245: shar gyi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:247: mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:248: bdud kyi rgyal po ti ti ti myag rje //
NG0801:249: phyag na bdud kyi gsod byed spu gri rnon po bsnams /
NG0801:250: shar lho mtshams nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:251: lho yi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:252: bdud kyi rgyal po khro bdag thod pa rje //
NG0801:253: phyag na bdud khram stag gi mgo can bsnams //
NG0801:254: lho yi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:255: lho nub mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:256: bdud kyi rgyal po dmu bdud brang dkar rje //
NG0801:257: phyag na shod kyi sgro ba mi 'gro can /
NG0801:258: khal du bong bu gwa pa lcags mthur can la bskyil //
NG0801:259: lho nub mtshams nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:260: nub kyi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:261: bdud kyi rgyal po tshangs pa bdud khro rje //
NG0801:262: phyag na bdud kyi dril zhags 'bar ba brnams //
NG0801:263: nub byang phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hum /
NG0801:264: nub byang mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:265: bdud kyi rgyal po ting ri mgo ston rje //
NG0801:266: phyag na bdud sha nag po'i thod pa bsnams //
NG0801:267: nub byang mtshams nas dgra bo khug la shog hu~m /
NG0801:268: byang gi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:269: bdud kyi rgyal po khro rje ru rgyal rje //
NG0801:270: phyag na bdud rta nag po mgo gcod bsnams //
NG0801:271: byang gi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:272: byang shar mtshams nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:273: bdud kyi rgyal po spyi bdud yam pa khro rje nag po rje //
NG0801:274: phyag na bdud kyi tr-i shul rtse gsum bsnams //
NG0801:275: byang shar mtshams bas dgra bo khug la shog / hu~m /
NG0801:276: 'og gi phyogs nas dgra bo 'gugs byed pa //
NG0801:277: bdud kyi rgyal po sa mdog nag po rje /
NG0801:278: phyag na chu srin phur pa gti mug phag mgo can //
NG0801:279: skyes 'gro thams cad gsod par byed //
NG0801:280: 'og gi phyogs nas dgra bo khug la shog / ma ra na dza dza /
NG0801:281: che ge mo ni ra ma ra ya rbad pu nan dza dza /
NG0801:282: zhes ni rbad de bla tshe dgug / bdud khros pa'i rgyud las /
NG0801:283: bstod bskul pho nya bdag pa'i le'u ste drug pa'o //  // yang dpal chen pos bka' stsal pa /
NG0801:284: lha rtags byung nas dgra rtags rnams //
NG0801:285: bul las de bag bul na //
NG0801:286: mi lus mo shing byang bu la //
NG0801:287: dril bu ste che dgu'i lcags la gzugs //
NG0801:288: de la thun gyis brabs te gsang *//
NG0801:289: mgo ba'i lha dang 'di yis dbye //
NG0801:290: 'bob dang khyi lud rwa ru dang *//
NG0801:291: zhabs ma gu gul za 'og bsregs //
NG0801:292: mtshan ma'i ming rus de la bdug / dgra lha pho lha yul lha dang *//
NG0801:293: mo lha srog lha rgyal po ste //
NG0801:294: rgyal rten phral la gsad par bya'o //
NG0801:296: spogs pa'i cho ga lha dang dbral ba'i le'u ste
NG0801:297: bdun pa'o // // de skad ces bka' stsal nas
NG0801:298: / dpa' bo chen po gtso bo dang 'khor ltar
NG0801:299: snang ba'i de nyid yang dag par mi snang bar
NG0801:300: / byas te / rtsa ba'i longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku la thim ste /
NG0801:301: chos kyi sku dang tha mi dad par gyur to //
NG0801:304: nyid kyang bstan pa bsrung ba'i don du nye bar 'khod de /
NG0801:305: legs nyes kyi gzu bo mdzad do //
NG0801:306: 'khor rnams kyang gtso bo la 'dud pa'i tshul gyis gnas par gyur to //
